  ('02642de8-a9ce-4801-b6a7-3140407680b6'::uuid, 'alexandria_official', 'already_enriched', 'https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/cali', 0.99, 'Cali Love', 'Alexandria Fragrances', null, 'EDP', array['Mandarin Orange', 'Pear', 'Ambrette', 'Benzoin', 'Musk']::text[], array['citrus', 'fruity', 'musk', 'amber']::text[], '{"top_notes":["Mandarin Orange","Pear"],"base_notes":["Ambrette","Benzoin","Musk"],"heart_notes":[],"source_name":"Cali Love","blocker_type":"source_gap","import_batch":"taxonomy_operationalization_pass9_tier4_batch2_source_repair_2026_05_22","source_brand":"Alexandria Fragrances","source_evidence":{"official_tags":["Ambrette","Benzoin","Mandarin Orange","Musk","Pear"],"source_gap_closure":{"issue":"No usable canonical notes, accords, pyramid, or source metadata existed before this pass.","action":"Closed the source gap using the exact official Alexandria product page for this fragrance.","repaired":true},"official_source_url":"https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/cali","contamination_repair":null,"official_description":"Introducing Cali Love, a fragrance that will transport you to the sunny beaches of California with just one spritz. Inspired by California Dreams LV, this bright and juicy scent will become your go-to for everyday wear. With fresh notes of Mandarin Orange and Pear, Cali Love provides a refreshing burst of energy that is perfect for a hot summer day. But Cali Love is more than just a simple fragrance. This scent has been thoughtfully crafted to provide unique benefits that will keep you coming back for more. Here are just a few key features and benefits of this amazing fragrance: Long-lasting scent: Cali Love is designed to last all day, so you can indulge in the fruity aroma from morning to night. Easy to wear: This fragrance isn''t overpowering, making it the perfect \"easy reach\" for any day. The light, airy notes are perfect for layering with other scents or wearing on their own. But that''s not all. Cali Love is also incredibly versatile, making it the perfect addition to your fragrance collection. Whether you''re heading to work, meeting up with friends for brunch, or lounging on the beach, Cali Love is the perfect accessory for any occasion. So what are you waiting for? Indulge in the California Dream with Cali Love. With its bright and juicy scent, long-lasting formula, and versatility, this fragrance is a must-have for anyone who loves to embrace life''s everyday moments. Try it today, and experience the magic of California in a bottle!","official_source_excerpt":"Official Alexandria page describes fresh mandarin orange and pear with official product tags for ambrette, benzoin, and musk.","official_source_confidence":0.99},"extraction_method":"manual_official_product_page_review","identity_match_status":"exact_official_product_page","official_source_import":true}'::jsonb, null, now(), now()),
  ('07aa9e75-b221-4b66-b991-56b2c3424f52'::uuid, 'alexandria_official', 'already_enriched', 'https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/leather-intense', 0.99, 'Leather Intense', 'Alexandria Fragrances', null, 'EDP', array['Leather', 'Rose', 'Oud', 'Woody Notes', 'Italian Orange', 'Tuscan Iris', 'Cedar', 'Sandalwood', 'Ambrette']::text[], array['leather', 'woody', 'floral', 'citrus', 'powdery', 'musk']::text[], '{"top_notes":["Italian Orange"],"base_notes":["Tuscan Iris","Cedar","Sandalwood","Ambrette"],"heart_notes":["Leather","Rose","Oud","Woody Notes"],"source_name":"Leather Intense","blocker_type":"source_gap","import_batch":"taxonomy_operationalization_pass9_tier4_batch2_source_repair_2026_05_22","source_brand":"Alexandria Fragrances","source_evidence":{"official_tags":["Ambrette","Cedar","Italian Orange","Leather","Oud","Rose","Sandalwood","Tuscan Iris"],"source_gap_closure":{"issue":"No usable canonical notes, accords, pyramid, or source metadata existed before this pass.","action":"Closed the source gap using the exact official Alexandria product page for this fragrance.","repaired":true},"official_source_url":"https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/leather-intense","contamination_repair":null,"official_description":"Introducing our Leather Intense fragrance, inspired by the iconic Dior Homme Parfum. Our scent exudes luxury and class, providing a sensual explosion that emanates a beautiful aroma. With eternal longevity and projection, you can rest assured that our product is curated to leave a lasting impression. Our Leather Intense fragrance features a realistic leather note, along with hints of rose, oud, and woody notes that make for a truly unique olfactory experience. The scent is rounded off with a spritz of Italian orange, which provides a perfect balance to the dark woods and raw leather notes. As for the base notes, Tuscan Iris brings a sort of powdery/barbershop/dapper feeling to this monster. It is perfect for special occasions when you want to feel absolutely luxurious and important. If you want to smell seriously great, Leather Intense is a must-have for every man looking to exude confidence and style. Our fragrance is perfect for night-time use or whenever you need a boost of confidence and luxury. Here are some key features and benefits of our product: - Long-lasting fragrance: With eternal longevity and projection, you can be assured that our product lasts throughout the day. - Strong and sexy: Our fragrance exudes an irresistible scent that is perfect for those who want to feel confident and sexy. - Perfect for special occasions: Whether it''s a wedding, business meeting, or a night out with friends, our fragrance is the perfect addition to your outfit. At Leather Intense, we believe in providing a product that stands out from the rest. Our fragrance is unique and one-of","official_source_excerpt":"Official Alexandria page describes leather, rose, oud, woody notes, Italian orange, and Tuscan iris, with official tags adding cedar, sandalwood, and ambrette.","official_source_confidence":0.99},"extraction_method":"manual_official_product_page_review","identity_match_status":"exact_official_product_page","official_source_import":true}'::jsonb, null, now(), now()),
  ('0846b785-b534-4f13-921c-1bd945f6c36d'::uuid, 'alexandria_official', 'already_enriched', 'https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/arabian-horse', 0.99, 'Arabian Horse', 'Alexandria Fragrances', null, 'UNKNOWN', array['Cinnamon', 'Peppercorn', 'Incense', 'Tobacco', 'Vanilla', 'Patchouli', 'Vetiver', 'Cedar', 'Labdanum', 'Musk']::text[], array['spicy', 'tobacco', 'gourmand', 'woody', 'incense', 'musk']::text[], '{"top_notes":["Cinnamon","Peppercorn"],"base_notes":["Patchouli","Vetiver","Cedar","Labdanum","Musk"],"heart_notes":["Incense","Tobacco","Vanilla"],"source_name":"Arabian Horse","blocker_type":"source_gap","import_batch":"taxonomy_operationalization_pass9_tier4_batch2_source_repair_2026_05_22","source_brand":"Alexandria Fragrances","source_evidence":{"official_tags":["Cedar","Cinnamon","Cypriol Oil","Incense","Iso E Super","Labdanum","Musk","Osmanthus","Parfums de Marly","Pepper","Tobacco","Vanilla","Vetiver"],"source_gap_closure":{"issue":"No usable canonical notes, accords, pyramid, or source metadata existed before this pass.","action":"Closed the source gap using the exact official Alexandria product page for this fragrance.","repaired":true},"official_source_url":"https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/arabian-horse","contamination_repair":null,"official_description":"The Arabian Horse fragrance from the Alexandria collection is an exquisite scent that is perfect for any man looking to impress. Inspired by Parfums de Marly''s Herod, this fragrance is a must-have for any gentleman''s fragrance collection. The fragrance opens with a tantalizing blend of cinnamon and peppercorns that instantly grabs your attention. It soon mellows down to a sweet and smoky heart of incense, tobacco, and vanilla, which leave you feeling relaxed and euphoric. The base is a harmonious fusion of patchouli and vetiver that adds a woody and earthy edge to the fragrance. One of the unique features of this fragrance is its all-season versatility. The creamy vanilla and sweet tobacco make it perfect for cold winter nights while the fresh cinnamon and peppercorns give it just the right touch of spice and energy to be worn during the summer months. Here are some benefits of the Arabian Horse fragrance that you don''t want to miss out on: - Long-lasting scent: The fragrance lasts for hours without ever being too overpowering. You can wear it to work or out on the town, and you''ll receive compliments wherever you go. - High-quality ingredients: Each fragrance is crafted using high-quality ingredients, ensuring that you get a luxury scent that is worth every penny. In conclusion, the Arabian Horse fragrance is an unbeatable blend of spice, sweet, and woodsy notes that exemplify elegance and masculinity. This fragrance is an excellent choice for any occasion and every season. Don''t miss out on your chance to add this must-have fragrance to your collection!","official_source_excerpt":"Official Alexandria page says Arabian Horse opens with cinnamon and peppercorns, moves to a heart of incense, tobacco, and vanilla, and dries down on patchouli and vetiver.","official_source_confidence":0.99},"extraction_method":"manual_official_product_page_review","identity_match_status":"exact_official_product_page","official_source_import":true}'::jsonb, null, now(), now()),
  ('0a69eee8-5c08-48b3-9c67-9f2b7d89ed6d'::uuid, 'alexandria_official', 'already_enriched', 'https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/hafez-1984-intense', 0.99, 'Hafez 1984 Intense', 'Alexandria Fragrances', null, 'UNKNOWN', array['Leather', 'Oud', 'Coffee', 'Tonka Bean', 'Vanilla', 'Jasmine', 'Saffron', 'Sandalwood']::text[], array['leather', 'gourmand', 'woody', 'spicy', 'floral', 'amber']::text[], '{"top_notes":[],"base_notes":[],"heart_notes":[],"source_name":"Hafez 1984 Intense","blocker_type":"source_gap","import_batch":"taxonomy_operationalization_pass9_tier4_batch2_source_repair_2026_05_22","source_brand":"Alexandria Fragrances","source_evidence":{"official_tags":["Coffee","Jasmine","Leather","Oud","Saffron","Sandalwood","Tonka Bean","Vanille"],"source_gap_closure":{"issue":"No usable canonical notes, accords, pyramid, or source metadata existed before this pass.","action":"Closed the source gap using the exact official Alexandria product page for this fragrance.","repaired":true},"official_source_url":"https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/hafez-1984-intense","contamination_repair":null,"official_description":"Indulge in the luxurious and captivating scent of Hafez 1984 Intense Original Creation! This unique fragrance is an original creation from Alexandria, Egypt and is the perfect scent for anyone who craves a dark, sweet, and sultry aroma. Hafez 1984 Intense is the ideal scent for the confident and mysterious person who wants to make a statement with their fragrance. Hafez 1984 Intense is a complex blend that combines essences of sultry leather, rich oud, and roasted coffee to deliver an indulgent and captivating scent. It is perfect for any occasion, any time of day, and especially suits cooler weather. The fragrance is bold and powerful, yet also has a subtle sweetness that comes from the addition of tonka bean, vanilla, and a hint of jasmine. Here are two key features and benefits of Hafez 1984 Intense: Unique aroma - Hafez 1984 Intense is an original creation that is distinct from other fragrances on the market. The combination of sweet and sultry scents makes this scent irresistible and unforgettable. Long-lasting - Hafez 1984 Intense is designed to stay on your skin long after you''ve applied it. One application is enough to last you all day or night. Anyone who wants to make an impression with their scent should add Hafez 1984 Intense Original Creation to their perfume collection. The fragrance is perfect for both men and women who want to exude confidence, sophistication, and sensuality. Order now and wrap yourself in the entrancing bouquet of beauty that is Hafez 1984 Intense!","official_source_excerpt":"Official Alexandria page describes sultry leather, rich oud, and roasted coffee with tonka bean, vanilla, jasmine, and official product tags for saffron and sandalwood.","official_source_confidence":0.99},"extraction_method":"manual_official_product_page_review","identity_match_status":"exact_official_product_page","official_source_import":true}'::jsonb, null, now(), now()),
  ('129404e3-107e-4bbe-a94c-7a17f5fa7923'::uuid, 'alexandria_official', 'already_enriched', 'https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/mango-hurricane', 0.99, 'Mango Hurricane', 'Alexandria Fragrances', null, 'EDP', array['Mandarin Orange', 'Lemon', 'Mango', 'Geranium', 'Musk', 'White Woods']::text[], array['citrus', 'fruity', 'floral', 'musk', 'woody']::text[], '{"top_notes":["Mandarin Orange","Lemon"],"base_notes":["Musk","White Woods"],"heart_notes":["Mango","Geranium"],"source_name":"MANGO HURRICANE","blocker_type":"source_gap","import_batch":"taxonomy_operationalization_pass9_tier4_batch2_source_repair_2026_05_22","source_brand":"Alexandria Fragrances","source_evidence":{"official_tags":[],"source_gap_closure":{"issue":"No usable canonical notes, accords, pyramid, or source metadata existed before this pass.","action":"Closed the source gap using the exact official Alexandria product page for this fragrance.","repaired":true},"official_source_url":"https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/mango-hurricane","contamination_repair":null,"official_description":"Refresh your senses with the vibrant and bold aroma of Mango Hurricane. Made for both men and women, this fragrance incorporates the refreshing scents of Mandarin Orange and Lemon, balanced out with the sweet and succulent notes of Mango and Geranium. The base notes of Musk and White Woods add a touch of sophistication to this irresistible scent.","official_source_excerpt":"Official Alexandria page says Mango Hurricane combines mandarin orange and lemon with mango and geranium over musk and white woods.","official_source_confidence":0.99},"extraction_method":"manual_official_product_page_review","identity_match_status":"exact_official_product_page","official_source_import":true}'::jsonb, null, now(), now()),
  ('2ab42ec3-8e42-4bbc-a655-ed43c5877c9e'::uuid, 'alexandria_official', 'already_enriched', 'https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/meraki', 0.99, 'It''s Never Too Late', 'Alexandria Fragrances', null, 'EDP', array['Wild Jasmine', 'White Flowers', 'Osmanthus', 'Raspberry', 'Cherry', 'Red Berries', 'Cardamom', 'Saffron', 'Nutmeg', 'Amber', 'Myrrh', 'Resins', 'Guaiac Wood', 'Cedarwood', 'Sandalwood', 'Golden Tobacco', 'Vanilla', 'Tonka Bean']::text[], array['floral', 'fruity', 'spicy', 'amber', 'resin', 'woody', 'gourmand']::text[], '{"top_notes":["Wild Jasmine","White Flowers","Osmanthus","Raspberry","Cherry","Red Berries"],"base_notes":["Guaiac Wood","Cedarwood","Sandalwood","Golden Tobacco","Vanilla","Tonka Bean"],"heart_notes":["Cardamom","Saffron","Nutmeg","Amber","Myrrh","Resins"],"source_name":"It''s Never Too Late","blocker_type":"source_gap","import_batch":"taxonomy_operationalization_pass9_tier4_batch2_source_repair_2026_05_22","source_brand":"Alexandria Fragrances","source_evidence":{"official_tags":[],"source_gap_closure":{"issue":"No usable canonical notes, accords, pyramid, or source metadata existed before this pass.","action":"Closed the source gap using the exact official Alexandria product page for this fragrance.","repaired":true},"official_source_url":"https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/meraki","contamination_repair":null,"official_description":"It''s Never Too Late Previously Known As Meraki Crafted with Passion, Worn with Purpose The fragrance opens with a delicate whisper of white flowers and wild jasmine, masterfully crafted by Rita Brena. Anna Chiara Di Trolio enhances its radiance with a fruity elegance of osmanthus, raspberry, cherry, and red berries, while Mariaceleste Lombardo introduces a rich, spicy heart featuring cardamom, saffron, and nutmeg. At its core, Patrizia Cezza weaves an opulent balsamic accord, enriched with resins, amber, and myrrh, creating a deep, luxurious warmth. The composition is anchored by the leathery richness of guaiac wood, the bold strength of cedarwood and sandalwood, and the golden tobacco accord, carefully blended by Dominique Moellhausen for a subtly smoky finish. Finally, Michelle Moellhausen’s touch brings a creamy and refined depth with the smooth, powdery richness of tonka bean and vanilla, lending a warm and gourmand allure. This intricate and expertly balanced creation, perfected by Moellhausen Perfumers in Dubai, is a fragrance designed to leave a lasting impression—an unforgettable olfactory signature that sets a new standard in perfumery. Top Notes: Wild jasmine, white flowers, osmanthus, raspberry, cherry, and red berries. Heart Notes: Cardamom, saffron, nutmeg, amber, myrrh, and resins. Base Notes: Guaiac wood, cedarwood, sandalwood, golden tobacco, vanilla, and tonka bean. Limited Edition: This carefully crafted fragrance is available now. Once the limited release is sold out, it may not return in this size or form.","official_source_excerpt":"Official Alexandria page provides a full It''s Never Too Late note pyramid with floral-fruity top notes, spicy amber-resin heart notes, and woody tobacco-vanilla-tonka base notes.","official_source_confidence":0.99},"extraction_method":"manual_official_product_page_review","identity_match_status":"exact_official_product_page","official_source_import":true}'::jsonb, null, now(), now()),
  ('352d8607-f732-4773-a26a-df9967e501c2'::uuid, 'alexandria_official', 'already_enriched', 'https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/lady-karina-inspired-by-pdm-oriana', 0.99, 'Lady Karina', 'Alexandria Fragrances', null, 'EDP', array['Mandarin Orange', 'Grapefruit', 'Bergamot', 'Orange Blossom', 'Marshmallow', 'Whipped Cream', 'Raspberry', 'Black Currant', 'Ambrette', 'Musk']::text[], array['citrus', 'fruity', 'floral', 'creamy', 'gourmand', 'musk']::text[], '{"top_notes":["Mandarin Orange","Grapefruit","Bergamot"],"base_notes":["Ambrette","Musk"],"heart_notes":["Orange Blossom","Marshmallow","Whipped Cream","Raspberry","Black Currant"],"source_name":"Lady Karina","blocker_type":"source_gap","import_batch":"taxonomy_operationalization_pass9_tier4_batch2_source_repair_2026_05_22","source_brand":"Alexandria Fragrances","source_evidence":{"official_tags":["Ambrette","Bergamot","Black Currant","Grapefruit","Mandarin Orange","Marshmallow","Musk","Orange Blossom","Raspberry","Whipped Cream"],"source_gap_closure":{"issue":"No usable canonical notes, accords, pyramid, or source metadata existed before this pass.","action":"Closed the source gap using the exact official Alexandria product page for this fragrance.","repaired":true},"official_source_url":"https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/lady-karina-inspired-by-pdm-oriana","contamination_repair":null,"official_description":"Indulge in a sweet treat that will whisk you away to a world of gourmand delights. Meet Lady Karina, the scent that is inspired by the luxurious PDM Oriana. This mesmerizing fragrance is the perfect accessory for any occasion. Prepare to be whisked away to a world of sweet floral aromas that are bound to captivate you. The scent of Lady Karina opens up with a zesty citrus burst of mandarin, grapefruit, and bergamot that will have you feeling refreshed and energized. Just when you thought it couldn''t get any better, top notes of fresh orange blossom and a heady rush of marshmallow, whipped cream and raspberry sizzle to perfection to overwhelm your senses. Let Lady Karina be your daily driver, with its irresistible fragrance that is perfect to wear anywhere at any time. So whether it''s a casual day out or a romantic evening, it is the perfect scent for every occasion. But, what sets Lady Karina apart? Here are the key features and benefits that make it a must-have. Long-Lasting scent: Lady Karina''s fragrance is made to withstand the test of time, and you can count on it lasting for hours on end. Adaptable: Perfect for any season, Lady Karina''s refreshing notes of citrus are bound to uplift you, while the sweet, floral, and gourmand notes add warmth to your winter days. So, take a chance on Lady Karina, and discover the world of gourmand scents. You won''t regret it!","official_source_excerpt":"Official Alexandria page describes a citrus burst of mandarin, grapefruit, and bergamot followed by orange blossom, marshmallow, whipped cream, and raspberry, with official tags adding black currant, ambrette, and musk.","official_source_confidence":0.99},"extraction_method":"manual_official_product_page_review","identity_match_status":"exact_official_product_page","official_source_import":true}'::jsonb, null, now(), now()),
