  ('410bc18e-1815-4fc5-9620-352e5501641a'::uuid, 'alexandria_official', 'already_enriched', 'https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/ritro-flare-silver', 0.99, 'Retro Flare (Silver)', 'Alexandria Fragrances', null, 'EDP', array['Juniper Berries', 'Coriander', 'Musk']::text[], array['aromatic', 'spicy', 'musk', 'woody']::text[], '{"top_notes":["Juniper Berries","Coriander"],"base_notes":["Musk"],"heart_notes":[],"source_name":"Retro Flare (silver)","blocker_type":"source_gap","import_batch":"taxonomy_operationalization_pass9_tier4_batch2_source_repair_2026_05_22","source_brand":"Alexandria Fragrances","source_evidence":{"official_tags":["Aromatic","Fresh Spicy","Musky","Soft Spicy","Woody"],"source_gap_closure":{"issue":"No usable canonical notes, accords, pyramid, or source metadata existed before this pass.","action":"Closed the source gap using the exact official Alexandria product page for this fragrance.","repaired":true},"official_source_url":"https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/ritro-flare-silver","contamination_repair":null,"official_description":"Introducing Retro Flare (silver), a fragrance that not only smells amazing but also transcends time. Inspired by Gentle Fluidity Silver, this retro-mazing scent captures the essence of fragrances of the past while incorporating modern twists to make it a powerhouse in the perfume industry. With notes of juniper berries, coriander, and musc, Retro Flare (silver) is a scent that is both masculine and gentle, providing an aroma that is both captivating and alluring. But what sets it apart from other perfumes on the market is its unique features and benefits. Here are just a few reasons why you should give Retro Flare (silver) a try: It is made with all-natural ingredients, making it a safe and healthy option for those that care about what they put on their bodies. Retro Flare (silver) has a unisex scent that enjoys the best of both worlds - it is masculine yet gentle, making it a versatile fragrance that can be worn by anyone. But what exactly makes Retro Flare (silver) stand out? Well, imagine wearing a scent that not only smells great but also takes you back to a simpler time, where fragrances were powerful, statement-making, and unforgettable. That''s what you get with Retro Flare (silver). Whether you''re looking for a scent for a night out on the town or just looking to spice up your daily routine, this iconic scent is perfect for any occasion. In conclusion, Retro Flare (silver) is a fragrance that is both timeless and modern. It captures the essence of fragrances from the past while still incorporating modern twists to make it even better. Its unique features and benefits","official_source_excerpt":"Official Alexandria page highlights juniper berries, coriander, and musc, while official tags classify the scent as aromatic, musky, fresh spicy, soft spicy, and woody.","official_source_confidence":0.99},"extraction_method":"manual_official_product_page_review","identity_match_status":"exact_official_product_page","official_source_import":true}'::jsonb, null, now(), now()),
  ('86190082-a4bd-4e7b-8d27-71db9a8ca737'::uuid, 'alexandria_official', 'already_enriched', 'https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/happiest-aoud', 0.99, 'Happiest Aoud', 'Alexandria Fragrances', null, 'EDP', array['Bergamot', 'Ginger', 'Herbal Notes', 'Oud', 'Licorice', 'Cedar', 'Musk', 'Vanilla']::text[], array['woody', 'spicy', 'aromatic', 'green', 'musk', 'gourmand']::text[], '{"top_notes":["Bergamot","Ginger"],"base_notes":["Cedar","Musk","Vanilla"],"heart_notes":["Herbal Notes","Oud","Licorice"],"source_name":"Happiest Aoud","blocker_type":"source_gap","import_batch":"taxonomy_operationalization_pass9_tier4_batch2_source_repair_2026_05_22","source_brand":"Alexandria Fragrances","source_evidence":{"official_tags":["Bergamot","Cedar","Ginger","Herbal Notes","Licorice","Musk","Oud","Vanilla"],"source_gap_closure":{"issue":"No usable canonical notes, accords, pyramid, or source metadata existed before this pass.","action":"Closed the source gap using the exact official Alexandria product page for this fragrance.","repaired":true},"official_source_url":"https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/happiest-aoud","contamination_repair":null,"official_description":"Introducing the fragrance that is bound to make you the happiest you''ve ever been - Happiest Aoud, inspired by the luxurious scent of Initio Oud For Happiness. This exquisite unisex fragrance is unlike any other on the market, offering a unique blend of herbaceous oud and zesty ginger that creates a powerful and long-lasting scent that sets you apart from the rest. One of the key features of Happiest Aoud is its all-day and all-night performance. This intoxicating fragrance will stay with you through every moment of your life, making it perfect for special occasions or a luxurious night out. Unlike other fragrances that fade away after a few hours, Happiest Aoud stands the test of time thanks to its powerful blend of botanicals and fresh ginger notes. But that''s not all. Happiest Aoud also boasts a unique candied oud note that gives it a sweet, sexy edge that''s sure to turn heads. This unique blend of sugar and oud creates a fragrance that feels both familiar and completely new, making it a must-have for anyone looking to make a statement. In addition to its intoxicating scent, Happiest Aoud offers a number of key benefits that make it a great addition to any fragrance collection. Here are just a few: - Long-lasting fragrance that stays with you all day and all night. - Unique blend of oud and ginger that sets you apart from the rest. - Unisex scent that''s perfect for any occasion. Whether you''re looking to make a statement at a party or simply elevate your daily fragrance routine, Happiest Aoud is the perfect choice. So why not try it for yourself and experience the happin","official_source_excerpt":"Official Alexandria page describes herbaceous oud, zesty ginger, and a candied oud effect, while official tags add bergamot, cedar, herbal notes, licorice, musk, and vanilla.","official_source_confidence":0.99},"extraction_method":"manual_official_product_page_review","identity_match_status":"exact_official_product_page","official_source_import":true}'::jsonb, null, now(), now()),
  ('91b7673f-6c2b-405a-83a6-af2083775b64'::uuid, 'alexandria_official', 'already_enriched', 'https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/mango-storm', 0.99, 'Mango Storm', 'Alexandria Fragrances', null, 'EDP', array['Apple', 'Mango', 'Pineapple', 'Bergamot', 'Ambergris', 'Oakmoss']::text[], array['fruity', 'citrus', 'green', 'mineral', 'woody']::text[], '{"top_notes":["Apple","Mango"],"base_notes":["Ambergris","Oakmoss"],"heart_notes":["Pineapple","Bergamot"],"source_name":"Mango Storm","blocker_type":"source_gap","import_batch":"taxonomy_operationalization_pass9_tier4_batch2_source_repair_2026_05_22","source_brand":"Alexandria Fragrances","source_evidence":{"official_tags":[],"source_gap_closure":{"issue":"No usable canonical notes, accords, pyramid, or source metadata existed before this pass.","action":"Closed the source gap using the exact official Alexandria product page for this fragrance.","repaired":true},"official_source_url":"https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/mango-storm","contamination_repair":null,"official_description":"Mango Storm – A Tropical Adventure Crafted with passion and precision, Mango Storm is more than just a fragrance 🟠 – it’s a journey of tropical elegance. This unisex scent begins with the crisp, refreshing notes of apple and mango, evoking a sense of fresh beginnings and endless possibilities. As it unfolds, dynamic middle notes of pineapple and bergamot burst forth, capturing the essence of sunlit tropical adventures. Finally, it settles into the grounding embrace of ambergris and oakmoss, a nod to nature’s timeless beauty and elegance. Fragrance Notes: • Top Notes: Apple, Mango • Middle Notes: Pineapple, Bergamot • Base Notes: Ambergris, Oakmoss Let Mango Storm transport you to a place where nature meets sophistication, leaving a lasting impression wherever you go.","official_source_excerpt":"Official Alexandria page provides a Mango Storm note pyramid of apple and mango, then pineapple and bergamot, over ambergris and oakmoss.",