  ('a600a58c-8e3f-41a6-ad66-ae61eda49141'::uuid, 'alexandria_official', 'already_enriched', 'https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/alexandrias-007', 0.99, 'Alexandria 007', 'Alexandria Fragrances', null, 'UNKNOWN', array['Cardamom', 'Coffee', 'Cinnamon', 'Nutmeg']::text[], array['spicy', 'gourmand', 'aromatic', 'woody']::text[], '{"top_notes":["Cardamom","Coffee"],"base_notes":["Cinnamon","Nutmeg"],"heart_notes":[],"source_name":"Alexandria''s ''007''","blocker_type":"source_gap","import_batch":"taxonomy_operationalization_pass9_tier4_batch2_source_repair_2026_05_22","source_brand":"Alexandria Fragrances","source_evidence":{"official_tags":["By Kilian","Cardamom","Cinnamon","Coffee","Nutmeg"],"source_gap_closure":{"issue":"No usable canonical notes, accords, pyramid, or source metadata existed before this pass.","action":"Closed the source gap using the exact official Alexandria product page for this fragrance.","repaired":true},"official_source_url":"https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/alexandrias-007","contamination_repair":null,"official_description":"Step into the world of espionage with Alexandria''s 007 fragrance, an aroma that exudes mystery and sophistication. Inspired by the intoxicating scent of By Kilian, this vintage fragrance will take you on a quest to captivate those around you with its unique blend of spicy and warm notes. At the heart of Alexandria''s 007 is a dominant note of cardamom, which pairs perfectly with the rich aroma of freshly brewed coffee. These top notes are perfectly balanced with the base notes of cinnamon and nutmeg, leaving behind a warm and inviting fragrance that is perfect for the modern man or woman. What sets Alexandria''s 007 apart is its versatility, making it perfect for both daytime and nighttime use. Whether you''re out running errands, meeting friends, or attending a formal event, this fragrance will make sure you stand out from the crowd. Here are just a few of the key features and benefits of Alexandria''s 007: The fragrance is perfect for all weathers, making it an ideal year-round scent for both men and women. The balanced blend of notes ensures the fragrance is both inviting and mysterious, making it the perfect scent to wear both day and night. If you''re looking for a fragrance that is as unique as you are, look no further than Alexandria''s 007. It''s a scent that will leave a lasting impression, whether you''re entertaining guests or just going about your daily routine. Let the intrigue and sophistication of this fragrance take you on a journey of epic proportions!","official_source_excerpt":"Official Alexandria page says cardamom and freshly brewed coffee lead the scent, balanced by base notes of cinnamon and nutmeg.","official_source_confidence":0.99},"extraction_method":"manual_official_product_page_review","identity_match_status":"exact_official_product_page","official_source_import":true}'::jsonb, null, now(), now()),
  ('abd1d78a-d24c-4930-9efa-c709231c8296'::uuid, 'alexandria_official', 'already_enriched', 'https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/dark-knight', 0.99, 'Dark Knight', 'Alexandria Fragrances', null, 'UNKNOWN', array['Rum', 'Dark Chocolate', 'Coffee', 'Vetiver', 'Patchouli', 'Sandalwood', 'Sugar Cane', 'Almond', 'Caramel', 'Heliotrope']::text[], array['boozy', 'gourmand', 'woody', 'spicy', 'powdery']::text[], '{"top_notes":["Rum","Dark Chocolate","Coffee"],"base_notes":["Sugar Cane","Almond","Caramel","Heliotrope"],"heart_notes":["Vetiver","Patchouli","Sandalwood"],"source_name":"Dark Knight","blocker_type":"source_gap","import_batch":"taxonomy_operationalization_pass9_tier4_batch2_source_repair_2026_05_22","source_brand":"Alexandria Fragrances","source_evidence":{"official_tags":["Almond","By Kilian","Caramel","Coffee","Dark Chocolate","Heliotrope","Rum","Sandalwood","Sugar Cane"],"source_gap_closure":{"issue":"No usable canonical notes, accords, pyramid, or source metadata existed before this pass.","action":"Closed the source gap using the exact official Alexandria product page for this fragrance.","repaired":true},"official_source_url":"https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/dark-knight","contamination_repair":null,"official_description":"Introducing our newest fragrance, Dark Knight, inspired by Kilian Black Phantom. 🟠 This seductive fragrance is perfect for anyone daring to explore the darker pleasures of life. With its unique blend of notes, Dark Knight is sure to leave a lasting impression wherever you go. Featuring unmistakable notes of rum and dark chocolate, this heady fragrance opens with a bold and unforgettable scent. As you explore deeper, you''ll discover a heart of vetiver and patchouli, mingling with creamy sandalwood to create a truly captivating experience. And finally, the sugar cane accord adds a touch of sweetness to the fragrance, making it the perfect balance of darkness and light. But that''s not all that Dark Knight has to offer. Here are a few key features and benefits of our newest fragrance: Long-lasting scent: Dark Knight is designed to last all day, letting you enjoy its captivating aroma for hours on end. Versatile fragrance: Whether you''re headed to work or out for a night on the town, Dark Knight is the perfect fragrance for any occasion. So why wait? Add Dark Knight to your collection today and experience the beguiling temptation that only this fragrance can offer. Whether you''re dressing up or dressing down, Dark Knight is sure to leave you feeling confident, bold, and daring. So don''t hesitate - try it today and explore the darker side of life!","official_source_excerpt":"Official Alexandria page highlights rum and dark chocolate, then a heart of vetiver and patchouli with creamy sandalwood and a sugar-cane accord, while official tags add almond, caramel, coffee, and heliotrope.","official_source_confidence":0.99},"extraction_method":"manual_official_product_page_review","identity_match_status":"exact_official_product_page","official_source_import":true}'::jsonb, null, now(), now()),
  ('c5106db2-f9d1-425b-9827-bdd28aea923a'::uuid, 'alexandria_official', 'already_enriched', 'https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/kid-in-candy-store', 0.99, 'Kid in Candy Store', 'Alexandria Fragrances', null, 'EDP', array['Milk', 'Strawberry', 'Sour Cherry', 'Bitter Almond', 'Black Currant', 'Caramel', 'Raspberry', 'Whipped Cream', 'Jasmine', 'Rose', 'Violet', 'Plum', 'Turkish Rose', 'Jasmine Sambac', 'Sugar', 'Vanilla', 'Musk', 'Sandalwood', 'Roasted Tonka Bean', 'Peru Balsam', 'Benzoin', 'Cinnamon', 'Cloves', 'Cedar', 'Patchouli', 'Vetiver']::text[], array['fruity', 'gourmand', 'creamy', 'floral', 'musk', 'spicy']::text[], '{"top_notes":["Milk","Strawberry","Sour Cherry","Bitter Almond","Black Currant"],"base_notes":["Sugar","Vanilla","Musk","Sandalwood","Roasted Tonka Bean","Peru Balsam","Benzoin","Cinnamon","Cloves","Cedar","Patchouli","Vetiver"],"heart_notes":["Caramel","Raspberry","Whipped Cream","Jasmine","Rose","Violet","Plum","Turkish Rose","Jasmine Sambac"],"source_name":"Kid in Candy Store","blocker_type":"source_gap","import_batch":"taxonomy_operationalization_pass9_tier4_batch2_source_repair_2026_05_22","source_brand":"Alexandria Fragrances","source_evidence":{"official_tags":["new-arrivals"],"source_gap_closure":{"issue":"No usable canonical notes, accords, pyramid, or source metadata existed before this pass.","action":"Closed the source gap using the exact official Alexandria product page for this fragrance.","repaired":true},"official_source_url":"https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/kid-in-candy-store","contamination_repair":null,"official_description":"Kid In Candy Store Indulge in the delightful charm of Kid In Candy Store , an original unisex creation by Hani, inspired by his extensive experiences with fragrances. This scent captures the sweet and playful essence of childhood dreams, blending fruity, floral, and creamy notes into a symphony of delight. Fragrance Profile: • Top Notes: Milk, Strawberry, Sour Cherry, Bitter Almond, Black Currant • Middle Notes: Caramel, Raspberry, Whipped Cream, Jasmine, Rose, Violet, Plum, Turkish Rose, Jasmine Sambac • Base Notes: Sugar, Vanilla, Musk, Sandalwood, Roasted Tonka Bean, Peru Balsam, Benzoin, Cinnamon, Cloves, Cedar, Patchouli, Vetiver Kid In Candy Store opens with a bright and refreshing burst of milk, strawberry, sour cherry, bitter almond, and black currant. The heart reveals a delicate mix of caramel, raspberry, whipped cream, jasmine, rose, violet, plum, Turkish rose, and jasmine sambac, adding a touch of elegance and whimsy. The base notes of sugar, vanilla, musk, sandalwood, roasted tonka bean, Peru balsam, benzoin, cinnamon, cloves, cedar, patchouli, and vetiver provide a comforting and long-lasting finish. This enchanting unisex fragrance is perfect for those who cherish the playful and joyful moments of life. Embrace the magic of Kid In Candy Store and let it transport you to a world of sweet indulgence.","official_source_excerpt":"Official Alexandria page provides a full Kid in Candy Store note pyramid spanning milky fruits, caramel-cream florals, and a rich sugary vanilla-tonka-woods base.","official_source_confidence":0.99},"extraction_method":"manual_official_product_page_review","identity_match_status":"exact_official_product_page","official_source_import":true}'::jsonb, null, now(), now()),
  ('d1947358-c00d-45f5-9461-55be6b87c14d'::uuid, 'alexandria_official', 'already_enriched', 'https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/hafez-three-inspired-by-roja-de-la-nuy-n3', 0.99, 'Thrḕ', 'Alexandria Fragrances', null, 'EDP', array['Bergamot', 'Rose', 'Artemisia', 'Leather', 'Nagarmotha', 'Sandalwood', 'Juniper', 'Cedar', 'Patchouli', 'Guaiac Wood', 'Amyris', 'Saffron', 'Amber', 'Labdanum', 'Balsam', 'Benzoin', 'Incense']::text[], array['amber', 'spicy', 'woody', 'incense', 'leather', 'floral', 'resin']::text[], '{"top_notes":["Bergamot"],"base_notes":["Leather","Nagarmotha","Sandalwood","Juniper","Cedar","Patchouli","Guaiac Wood","Amyris","Saffron","Amber","Labdanum","Balsam","Benzoin","Incense"],"heart_notes":["Rose","Artemisia"],"source_name":"Thrḕ","blocker_type":"source_gap","import_batch":"taxonomy_operationalization_pass9_tier4_batch2_source_repair_2026_05_22","source_brand":"Alexandria Fragrances","source_evidence":{"official_tags":["Amber","Amirys","Artemisia Leather","Balsam","Benzoin","Bergamot","CEdar","Guaiac Wood","Incense","Juniper","Labdanum","Nagarmotha","Patchouli","Rose","Saffron","Sandalwood"],"source_gap_closure":{"issue":"No usable canonical notes, accords, pyramid, or source metadata existed before this pass.","action":"Closed the source gap using the exact official Alexandria product page for this fragrance.","repaired":true},"official_source_url":"https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/hafez-three-inspired-by-roja-de-la-nuy-n3","contamination_repair":null,"official_description":"Looking for a fragrance that''s complex, unique, and absolutely breathtaking? Look no further than Thrḕ, the latest scent inspired by Roja N3. This fragrance is perfect for evening wear or cold days when you want to feel cozy and warm. What makes Thrḕ so special? For one thing, it''s blended with a range of incredible ingredients, including rose, woods, and incense. Each of these natural scents has its own benefits, creating a multi-layered and nuanced fragrance that shifts with every minute it''s on your skin. But that''s not all. Thrḕ also contains a range of other ingredients that help to make it truly special. There''s some citrus from the bergamot added in at the start, for a refreshing burst of energy as you first apply it. Then, as the fragrance starts to dry down, the rose and artemisia come to the fore, creating a beautiful, floral middle note that''s sweet and seductive. And that''s not all. Thrḕ is designed to be long-lasting, so you can enjoy the scent all night long. The base is made up of a range of ingredients that help to hold the fragrance together, including leather, nagarmotha, sandalwood, juniper, cedar, patchouli, guaiac wood, amirys, saffron, amber, labdanum, balsam, benzoin, and incense. All of these work together to create a rich, complex, and sensual fragrance that''s totally unique. Looking for some key features and benefits? Here are just a few: Multi-layered fragrance that shifts with every minute it''s on your skin Long-lasting scent that''s perfect for evening wear or cold days So why wait? Try Thrḕ today and start experiencing the incredible pleasure an","official_source_excerpt":"Official Alexandria page describes bergamot at the start, rose and artemisia in the middle, and a long leather-wood-resin-spice base with amber, labdanum, balsam, benzoin, and incense.","official_source_confidence":0.99},"extraction_method":"manual_official_product_page_review","identity_match_status":"exact_official_product_page","official_source_import":true}'::jsonb, null, now(), now()),
  ('d8905cfc-ffe3-4be4-8a73-01e78566d0ef'::uuid, 'alexandria_official', 'already_enriched', 'https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/cookie-monster-original-creation', 0.99, 'Cookie Monster', 'Alexandria Fragrances', null, 'UNKNOWN', array['Lotus Biscuit', 'Cinnamon', 'Buttery Notes', 'Caramel', 'Tonka Bean', 'Vanilla', 'Amber', 'Musk']::text[], array['gourmand', 'spicy', 'creamy', 'amber', 'musk']::text[], '{"top_notes":["Lotus Biscuit","Cinnamon","Buttery Notes"],"base_notes":["Amber","Musk"],"heart_notes":["Caramel","Tonka Bean","Vanilla"],"source_name":"Cookie Monster","blocker_type":"source_gap","import_batch":"taxonomy_operationalization_pass9_tier4_batch2_source_repair_2026_05_22","source_brand":"Alexandria Fragrances","source_evidence":{"official_tags":["new-arrivals"],"source_gap_closure":{"issue":"No usable canonical notes, accords, pyramid, or source metadata existed before this pass.","action":"Closed the source gap using the exact official Alexandria product page for this fragrance.","repaired":true},"official_source_url":"https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/cookie-monster-original-creation","contamination_repair":null,"official_description":"Indulge in the delectable scent of Cookie Monster , an original creation from our fragrance house. This unisex fragrance perfectly captures the irresistible aroma of freshly baked cookies, blending warm, spicy, and sweet notes that will make you feel cozy and nostalgic. Fragrance Profile: • Top Notes: Lotus Biscuit, Cinnamon, Buttery Notes • Middle Notes: Caramel, Tonka Bean, Vanilla • Base Notes: Amber, Musk Cookie Monster opens with the delightful, crunchy aroma of Lotus biscuits, enhanced by the warm spiciness of cinnamon and rich buttery notes. The heart of the fragrance brings a sweet, gourmand blend of caramel, tonka bean, and vanilla, evoking the comforting sweetness of freshly baked treats. Finally, the base notes of amber and musk add a touch of warmth and depth, creating a long-lasting and inviting scent. This fragrance is more than just a perfume; it’s a celebration of cherished moments and the simple joys of life. Wear Cookie Monster to bring a smile to your face and a spark of warmth to your day, making every moment a little more special. Experience the magic of Cookie Monster – a scent that’s as delightful and comforting as your favorite cookies.","official_source_excerpt":"Official Alexandria page provides a full Cookie Monster note pyramid with lotus biscuit, cinnamon, buttery notes, caramel, tonka bean, vanilla, amber, and musk.","official_source_confidence":0.99},"extraction_method":"manual_official_product_page_review","identity_match_status":"exact_official_product_page","official_source_import":true}'::jsonb, null, now(), now()),
  ('eed75bd3-af6d-48be-921e-fc82316e13a6'::uuid, 'alexandria_official', 'already_enriched', 'https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/alexandrias-united-kingdom', 0.99, 'Alexandria''s United Kingdom', 'Alexandria Fragrances', null, 'EDP', array['Ambergris', 'Balsam', 'Carrot Seeds', 'Cedar', 'Cloves', 'Guaiac Wood', 'Juniper', 'Labdanum', 'Leather', 'Musk', 'Oakmoss', 'Orris', 'Patchouli']::text[], array['leather', 'woody', 'musk', 'powdery', 'spicy', 'resin']::text[], '{"top_notes":[],"base_notes":[],"heart_notes":[],"source_name":"Alexandria''s United Kingdom","blocker_type":"contaminated_data","import_batch":"taxonomy_operationalization_pass9_tier4_batch2_source_repair_2026_05_22","source_brand":"Alexandria Fragrances","source_evidence":{"official_tags":["Ambergris","Balsam","Carrot Seeds","Cedar","Cloves","Guaiac Wood","Juniper","Labdanum","Leather","Musk","Oakmoss","Orris","Patchouli","pinch of Royalty"],"source_gap_closure":null,"official_source_url":"https://alexandriafragrances.com/products/alexandrias-united-kingdom","contamination_repair":{"issue":"Existing canonical notes or accords contained prose fragments, placeholders, SEO copy, or malformed text that could not be used as taxonomy evidence.","action":"Replaced contaminated scent structure with clean official-source-backed notes and accords from the exact Alexandria product page.","repaired":true},"official_description":"Looking for a fragrance that will transport you to the high society of Great Britain? Look no further than Alexandria’s United Kingdom, inspired by the famed Roja Doves Great Britain fragrance. With its pure, raw power, this fragrance embodies the essence of luxury and sophistication. The Rolls Royce leather seat scent is simply magical, creating a lasting and exotic impression wherever you go. Here are just a few of the many reasons to try Alexandria’s United Kingdom: High-quality materials: Made with only the finest materials available, Alexandria’s United Kingdom is a fragrance that truly stands apart. Every spray will envelop you in a world of leather, herbal and floral notes that captivate the senses. Lasting power: Tired of fragrances that fade after just a few hours? Alexandria’s United Kingdom is designed to last, giving you an unforgettable scent that will stay with you all day long. If you’re looking for the perfect winter fragrance, Alexandria’s United Kingdom is an absolute must-have. With its ability to cut through the cold and leave you feeling warm and cozy, this is a scent that is perfect for those chilly nights out on the town. So why wait? Whether you’re looking for a way to treat yourself or you’re searching for the perfect gift for that special someone, Alexandria’s United Kingdom is the perfect choice. With its unique blend of luxury, power and sophistication, this is a fragrance that is sure to turn heads and leave a lasting impression. Try it for yourself today and discover the magic of Great Britain!","official_source_excerpt":"Official Alexandria page describes leather, herbal, and floral character, while official product tags identify ambergris, balsam, carrot seeds, cedar, cloves, guaiac wood, juniper, labdanum, leather, musk, oakmoss, orris, and patchouli.","official_source_confidence":0.99},"extraction_method":"manual_official_product_page_review","identity_match_status":"exact_official_product_page","official_source_import":true}'::jsonb, null, now(), now())
